Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nagi Sanzenin, 13 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sagittarius with blood type AB.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My birthstone is turquoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awful! It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, my precious butler's been \Nkidnapped by some bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, since it's come to this, \NI'll transform into Mask the Money
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll smack the bad guys with 150 \Nmillion yen, duralumin case and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the warrior of love, \Ncourage, money, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and also of friendship, \Nhard work, and victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of money, Mask \Nthe Money will punish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take approximately 40 \Nyears to pay that back in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, given how much it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you work \Nout a reasonable repayment plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No interest, no collateral, and \Nrepayment contingent on your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No financial institution would \Nloan you 150 million like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful. There's \Nno reason to resent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please don't worry. I {\i1}am{\i0} grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your smile is twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:14.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hayate found himself trembling anew \Nat the overwhelming amount he owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like spring is still a long way away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:20.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:23.36,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:27.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:32.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:36.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:39.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like spring is still a long way away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:52.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:52.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:59.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:03.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:07.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:07.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:11.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:21.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:21.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:30.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:30.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:37.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:37.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:49.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:49.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:56.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:56.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:03.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:03:03.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Beast, the Robot, and the Butler that Shouted\N or Maybe Didn't Shout Love at the Heart of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? There are only 3 people \Nliving on this estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even among our secondary residences, \Nthis one is particularly small,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we don't need that many servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so this place is small...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when there are so few people, \Nit makes me feel even more tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I'm going to be \Nliving here, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how vast this place is,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the situation of being under \None roof with a cute girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You idiot, don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be under one roof, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's not as if we're \Nsleeping in the same room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... But still, the \Nthought makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Makes his heart race?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, living together with \Na pretty girl like Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm warning you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever lay a hand on Maria, \NI'll do far more than just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use all 48 killer techniques \Nand 52 submission holds on you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll turn you into mince \Nmeat with the roller from hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, what do you mean \Nby "lay a hand" on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, with the end of \Nthe year coming up fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my new life began.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's already New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year sure was a terrible year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My home was utterly cleaned out,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Eviction Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}not even the table was spared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:50.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I couldn't muster the urge to \Nfind my parents, who ran out on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.17,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To Hayate\NA Christmas Present For You
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I accepted the Miss's kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:56.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and decided to work as a butler \Nat this Sanzenin estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount I owe is definitely huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm just going to work \Nhard, so I don't get fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Maria, I have a question...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't have a clear \Npicture of what my job is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a word...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you're Nagi's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm her pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a little joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll gradually come \Nto understand what your job is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so for the time being, would \Nyou please go wake up Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:35.47,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep things neat and tidy.\NFloor Layout (2nd Floor)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Study, piano room, homework \Nroom, reading room, wardrobe room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,plus a PlayStation room, a Dreamcast \Nroom, and an N64 room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any point in keeping these separate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get up soon, your \Nwonderful breakfast will get cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down. Calm down, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:04.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible. It must be a 1:1 scale \Nmodel made by Kaiyodo or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's got to be Sony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:10.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be Sony's new model of \Nthe AIBO or the PlayStation 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man, Sony's world renowned \Ntechnology sure is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to wake me up? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, just that, behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no wonder it was hot. So you \Nwere sleeping with me, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tama?! He's enormous and \Nyou treat him like a cat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Tama, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wake up soon, \Nyour breakfast will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:42.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, don't! Such behavior will result \Nin you becoming his breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just woke up! Don't stare at me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not it! That might be what \Nour older audience is doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but that's not the issue right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem awfully shocked by Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful! Really! You are truly \Npitiful, Hayate Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, you still hadn't met...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the head butler of \Nthe Sanzenin household.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head butler? In other \Nwords, you're my superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, now's not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, you're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? It's one measly cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A tiger. It's a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my chance to make a pointed \Ncomment after keeping quiet until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Miss says that it \Nis a cat, it is a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tama, whose zoological \Nname is Whitetigerneko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you just said it was a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gigantic, vicious-looking beast \Nlike this needs to be caged quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that long-winded \Nremark has offended Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll warn you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama is a stupid cat, who is only \Nfriendly towards the Miss and Maria!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who offends this idiot \Nbecomes his victim immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean that he isn't \Nfriendly towards you, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true... Right, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tama, enough with the rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! What a huge commotion \Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Miss. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, as a cat of the Sanzenin family, \Nyou should keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you! Don't get too carried away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:54.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclamen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think this is my first \Ntime fighting a savage beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but my parents once told me, \N"We'll give you meat to eat,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I ended up breaking into a safari park
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stealing meat from the \Nlions on a regular basis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Hayate for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he can play \Nwith Tama as an equal, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of how many butler candidates \Nhave fallen in defeat before Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate will be able to \Nwin, even against Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if he cannot, I shall \Nconsider him a failure as a butler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have him leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! You can fire \Nhim or do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't win barehanded against \Na tiger, I'll be out of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the safari park, all I did \Nwas basically run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I should've died on \Nthat Christmas Day anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to try my best, so \NI don't disappoint her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has been bothering \Nme for a while now, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The area that they are fighting in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the cyclamens are \Nflowering beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:20.33,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(131,211)}Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I give up, I give up! I give up, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, there's no way a person \Ncan win barehanded against a tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, give me a \Npsychogun or a prog knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:26.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put great care into \Nraising the flowers here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I have repeatedly told \Nyou not to play in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:42.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cycla men
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or were you egged on by the two upstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying if Hayate couldn't win against Tama,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would be fired because he's \Nnot qualified as a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will get to you once I finish \Ntreating Hayate's wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so would you mind waiting a \Nlittle while for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yessir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a stern word with those two later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why in the world does \Nshe have a pet tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot happened and he has nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but there are lots \Nof places, like zoos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed to say, the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.13,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi took him in when he became \Nseparated from his parents in Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and after that, Tama was literally \Npampered like a kitten...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuzaka beef, top quality fatty \Ntuna, massages 3 times a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became so used to luxuries, \Nit would put humans to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So never mind the wild, he couldn't \Neven handle life at a zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he will never harm Nagi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he would surely risk \Nhis life to fight for Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a very good understanding about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows what would've happened \Nif he hadn't met Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he hadn't met her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So I guess you're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lump me together with a loser like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Looking so damn poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get run over by a Mars rover and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't tell the Miss and \Nthe others than I can talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.63,0:12:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pets belonging to rich folks can talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having grown up surrounded with love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:45.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tama apparently picked up human \Nspeech somewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:49.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But other than Hayate, no \None else knows of this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil's tongue noodles.\N({\u1}I{\u0}tokonnya{\u1}ku{\u0})
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scoundrel!\N({\u1}Ku{\u0}semo{\u1}no{\u0})
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.16,0:13:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I am against \Nmaking this person a butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the mustache that's \Nmaking these lame jokes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That hurts! My mustache!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the mustache, Klaus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That mustache is my pride and joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to hire him in \Nthanks for saving my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I promised to select \NHimegami's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something messed up about hiring \Na poor-looking boy in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, his face may have the \Nlook of poverty about him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it can have a calming effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate is the soothing type!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to be soothed that much, \Nyou should get a hamster or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! A hamster's too soothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's look of poverty is \Nactually just about right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy looks like he'll never \Nhave money luck in his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiring him will only bring \Nmisfortune to those around him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, they both do mean well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no knowing when you \Nmight become the target
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of another kidnapping like the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without the strength to protect his \Nmistress, even at the cost of his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot hire him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Protect my mistress, even \Nat the cost of my life...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strength, is it? Then there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, Hayate's body is uncommonly tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he was able to handle Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know, with \Nevery transformation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's combat abilities will \Nincrease by leaps and bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Hayate still has two stages \Nof transformation left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I have no such functionality!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not Frieza. Looking so \Ntroubled isn't going to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem with Hayate's \Nstrength or qualifications,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not give him an evaluation test?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evaluation test?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if he is truly capable \Nof protecting the Miss,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should even be able to swim across \Na pool of boiling hot coal tar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, a butler should definitely be fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if he's dropped from \Na height of 2000 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Um, what about what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall have the test prepared right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Bring it on! Do you worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Augh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I don't know \Nwhat I'm being tested on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but is it going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In more ways than one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, you'll be \Nable to manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.08,0:15:25.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyclamen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Maria, could it be the Miss \Nhas high expectations of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High... expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She tends to be extremely \Nshy around strangers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she doesn't openly show \Nher emotions very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, she's been smiling \Nless after Himegami left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's been a while since \Nshe was that energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you saved her \Nmust have really delighted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:59.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Part of me is definitely \Ndoing it for the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:02.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if she's putting her faith in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I decided that I wanted to \Nlive up to her expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, are you prepared for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the test that will \Nevaluate how qualified you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently being developed by a company \Ncontrolled by the Sanzenin family,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is the caregiver robot "Eight"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for \Nyou, Mr. Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you expect \Nme to fight this thing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so crass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a caregiver robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the ultimate \Nbutler, born to serve his master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will use these various \Nitems from daily life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you and Eight will compete to \Nsee who is the superior butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know... This is \Nan awfully ugly robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is technically the world's \Nmost cutting-edge caregiver robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most cutting-edge?! This thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If an ugly robot like this \Nwas taking care of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you actually want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this robot doesn't seem capable \Nof combining or transforming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Hayate would lose. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you want to see combining \Nor transforming that badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how about I transform you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, what a terribly \Nshort-tempered cutting-edge robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is no time for that! \NPlease hurry up and shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.62,0:17:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my ardent pathos is set \Nin motion, no one can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, as I recall, to stop it, \Nyou have to open the back panel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and enter the password 1-1-9-2...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, it'll apparently \Nstop if you just break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is going in that \Ndirection, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right! I have to protect the Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:05.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For I'm... I'm to be her butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to fight in earnest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, please step over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is this guy really for caregiving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.42,0:18:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a feature necessary \Nfor women living alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, stalkers seem to be a big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds absurdly fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, don't think you can keep \Nrunning away from me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the water pipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Machines are weak against water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who's going to clean up this mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waterproofing on Japanese \Nrobots is the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:03.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pure silver knives, which conduct \Nelectricity better than stainless steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, underfoot is a \Nwool carpet soaked with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is 100 volts of pure domestic power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, if you use that \Nunder these circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be electrocuted, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently a butler's \Nduty to protect his mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it costs his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act cool all you want. You're going \Nto be poor for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Collider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's a Collider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:50.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you kids out there, \Ndon't ever do this at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acquitted himself rather \Nbrilliantly, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still find Hayate's \Nabilities dissatisfactory?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can employ him at least \Nuntil we find our next butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, with the tolling \Nof the New Year's Eve bells,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the new year is finally almost \Nupon the Japanese archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye to the last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello to the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hope that the new year \Nis a good year for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're awake! I was worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What happened to the butler test?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I made such a mess of that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of other rooms \Nthat will serve as replacements.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no replacement for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! So, well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was happy that you protected me. So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll continue...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to count on you, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please leave it to me, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:25.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are still a lot of problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:28.26,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it seems he should continue \Nto do well at this estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, I swore to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I would protect this person, the \NMiss, even if it cost me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you there! Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for going \Non and on for 3 whole episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The cherry blossoms \Nhave all scattered already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us continue where we left off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting next episode is a new development!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.36,0:22:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This showdown sequence has been put \Noff since the start of Episode 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this will finally be the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New development!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, the boy became a legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.55,0:22:19.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, he became a butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:23.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, he will fight with a giant campus!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Moshi boku no yume ga kimi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:31.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If my dreams have taken your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kizutsuke-tetara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:36.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And brought it pain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:41.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sono omoi wa itsuka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:41.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, that anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:45.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Boku ga morau yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:45.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take from you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:51.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Taisetsu na mono ni furue-nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:51.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While trembling over something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kakezuri-mawatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And madly dashing about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Seou itami ni hibi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The hurt I bore made the days
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:07.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muimi ni sugita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:07.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go by emptily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oikaketa mama de oikosare-tsuzuke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:13.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just chasing and continually being overtaken
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:18.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohou ni kureru kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:18.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind who's lost its bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi no doko ni furetara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you should I touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:28.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ii ka o sagashita
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:28.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I sought it out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:33.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mamoritai yo kimi dake wa tsuyoku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:33.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You alone, I want to protect so much
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yokubou no wadachi kara touzakatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:39.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting away from the rut of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:44.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Itsuka subete te ni ireru sore ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:44.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, it will all be ours and that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:48.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimi to boku no Proof
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:48.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our proof, yours and mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:58.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Namida mo zenbu azukeru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:58.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Even all my tears, I entrust to you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:02.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.46,0:24:04.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a Hakuou student, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:22.97,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:05.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:06.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.53,0:24:08.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:09.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't said anything yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:13.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Hayate have become involved \Nin something troublesome again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:14.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:18.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"My First Errand. This \NIs Snake. No Response".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.43,0:24:21.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki, if you don't try to get \Nwhat you want once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:22.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll miss your chance at happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:25.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever felt the cosmos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.00,0:24:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My First Errand\N~This Is Snake. No Response{second line}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.93,0:24:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SIGN: If you don't watch "Hayate the Combat \NButler" again next time, I'll get mad.
